<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'/>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">
    <img class="cover-img" src="/images/generic.jpg" alt="background-img">
    <div class="cover"></div>
    <div class="content-box">
        <p class="title-text">
            <span>Welcome</span>
            <span>R inc</span>
        </p>
        <p class="sub-title">beyond human for humanity & for engineer</p>
        <div class="login-box">
            <form action="/login" method="post">
                <input type="text" name="id" placeholder="ID">
                <input type="password" name="pw" placeholder="Password">
                <input type="submit" value="SIGN IN">
                <p class="check-login-status">
                    <input type="checkbox"><span>로그인 상태 유지</span>
                </p>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="login-box-sub">
            <a href="#">R inc ID 또는 암호를 잊으셨습니까?</a>
            <a href="#">R inc ID 가 없으신가요? <span class="text-highlight">지금만드세요.</span></a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="copyright">Copyright ⓒ 2017 <span class="text-highlight">R inc</span></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
